se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.api.generator.parser

Enum PomToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PomToken>
      • se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.api.generator.parser.PomToken
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PomToken>

    public enum PomToken
extends Enum<PomToken>
    Enumeration of a set of standardized tokens normally usable within a Maven POM. All supplied tokens relate to typical properties used within POMs.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ARTIFACTID
      The artifactId for the active project.
      GROUPID
      The groupId for the active project.
      MODULES
      The fully populated modules XML element, usable only in REACTOR and ROOT_REACTOR poms.
      PARENT_ARTIFACTID
      The artifactId of the parent to the active maven project.
      PARENT_GROUPID
      The groupId of the parent to the active maven project.
      PARENT_POM_RELATIVE_PATH
      The relative path between the active maven project and its parent POM.
      PARENT_VERSION
      The maven version of the parent to the active maven project.
      RELATIVE_DIRPATH
      The relative path from the VCS project root to the active maven project.
      RELATIVE_PACKAGE
      The relative path from the VCS project root to the active maven project, with all '/' path delimiters replaced with '.'.
      VERSION
      The maven version for the active project.
